			<p>
				The website may use third-party tools for hosting, forms, analytics, and communications.
				Your use of those services may also be subject to their terms and policies.
			</p>

			<h2>Contact</h2>
			<p>
				If you have questions about these terms, contact
				<a href="mailto:riznewhite@gmail.com">riznewhite@gmail.com</a>.
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</BaseLayout>
